from flask import Flask, request, jsonify
from utils.auth import Auth
from utils.marketplace import search_marketplace
import logging

# ConfiguraciÃ³n de logging
logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)

app = Flask(__name__)

# Inicializar autenticaciÃ³n
auth = Auth()

@app.route('/api/buscar-marketplace', methods=['POST'])
def buscar_marketplace():
    data = request.json
    query = data.get('query')
    ubicacion = data.get('ubicacion')
    precio_max = data.get('precio_max')

    # Realizar bÃºsqueda en Marketplace
    resultados = search_marketplace(query, ubicacion, precio_max, auth.get_cookies())
    return jsonify(resultados)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(debug=True)

import requests
from playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright

class Auth:
    def __init__(self):
        self.cookies = None

    def login(self, email, password):
        with sync_playwright() as p:
            browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)
            page = browser.new_page()
            page.goto('https://www.facebook.com/login')
            page.fill('input[name="email"]', email)
            page.fill('input[name="pass"]', password)
            page.click('button[name="login"]')
            page.wait_for_navigation()
            self.cookies = page.context.cookies()
            browser.close()

    def get_cookies(self):
        return self.cookies

response_data.contenido:
import requests
from playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright

class Auth:
    def __init__(self):
        self.cookies = None

    def login(self, email, password):
        with sync_playwright() as p:
            browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)
            page = browser.new_page()
            page.goto('https://www.facebook.com/login')
            page.fill('input[name="email"]', email)
            page.fill('input[name="pass"]', password)
            page.click('button[name="login"]')
            page.wait_for_navigation()
            self.cookies = page.context.cookies()
            browser.close()

    def get_cookies(self):
        return self.cookies

from flask import Flask, request, jsonify
from utils.auth import Auth
from utils.marketplace import search_marketplace
import logging

# ConfiguraciÃ³n de logging
logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)

app = Flask(__name__)

# Inicializar autenticaciÃ³n
auth = Auth()

@app.route('/api/buscar-marketplace', methods=['POST'])
def buscar_marketplace():
    data = request.json
    query = data.get('query')
    ubicacion = data.get('ubicacion')
    precio_max = data.get('precio_max')

    # Realizar bÃºsqueda en Marketplace
    resultados = search_marketplace(query, ubicacion, precio_max, auth.get_cookies())
    return jsonify(resultados)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(debug=True)
